<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ذ أر:</span> <span class="c2">(ذَئِرَ)</span> اجْتَرَأَ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«ذَئِرَ النِّسَاءُ عَلَى أَزْوَاجِهِنَّ»</span> . بِكَسْرِ الْهَمْزَةِ أَيْ نَفَرْنَ وَنَشَزْنَ وَاجْتَرَأْنَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>